name: Individual Cards
description: Shout a big GENERIC MESSAGE to someone you give a shit about in card form. You can choose from a selection found here. Just specify which card you would like in paypal. Cards are A6 Epson printed Includes one red envelope Will be packaged in plastic with a Two Squares insert. We also sell packs of cards of your choice.

name: Pack of Four Cards
description: Show your someone that you care about them and stuff with a set of Two Squares cards. You can see our selection here. Specify which four cards you would like, you can choose any combination of cards (including duplicates) and we'll print on demand and deliver. Just put your choice in the notes as you pay in Paypal. 4 A6 cards Epson printed Includes 4 red envelopes Each card will be packaged individually in plastic with a Two Squares insert. We also sell cards individually.

name: Moz
description: Moz monsters come from Monster Island in Japan, but they were bored of that shit hole and decided they wanted to get out and travel the world. Each Moz has a name and a little fact about their likes and dislikes. Generally he just wants to be your friend and hang out. You can view our current selection on our Flickr page here, and make your final selection from the drop down menu below. Pictured: This is Bonnie. She likes running away and wearing nice clothes. She hates people who can't spell. Moz orders are back to normal, all orders are going out next day again.
